@startuml 40-keyboard-navigation
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title Keyboard Navigation

actor User
participant "HomePage" as UI
participant "SearchResultsPage" as SR
participant "Angular router" as R
participant "Focus ring CSS" as F

User -> UI: press Tab
UI -> F: focus -> logo
F --> User: visible ring (>=3:1)
User -> UI: Tab
UI -> F: focus -> notifications
User -> UI: Tab
UI -> F: focus -> profile
User -> UI: Tab
UI -> F: focus -> search input
User -> UI: type query, press Enter
UI -> R: navigate /search?q=...
R --> SR: mount
SR -> F: focus -> back / featured result
User -> SR: Tab through featured / results / bottom nav
User -> SR: Enter on featured result
SR -> R: navigate /contacts/:id

note right of F
  No outline:none without
  a replacement ring.
  Button Primary (gradient) uses
  $accent-tertiary ring at 2px.
end note

@enduml
